Naked women, all night parties and raging hormones mean only one thing - Spring Break! For UCLA student Larry Wilson, the real fun is just beginning. After Larry rescues a hot, rich babe named Heather from being kidnapped, she offers him the best reward ever - sex! Only Larry's luck takes a turn for the worse when the kidnappers return - before he receives his reward! It's one crazy adventure after another as Larry goes from Palm Springs to the Spring Break capital of the world - Fort Lauderdale.
